templateAssets.content: Due to high demand, admission to SDSU is highly competitive. General admission information is available at: http://arweb.sdsu.edu/es/admissions/transfers/index.html.
Vocal majors must take MUSIC 243. Keyboard majors are exempt from MUSIC 110A -MUSIC 110B, and will substitute MUSIC 211A- MUSIC 211B for  MUSIC 210A- MUSIC 210B.

items.courseTitle: Music Appreciation: Music in Western Cultures
